# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s10d_7c7ec771:

    # "Going down the hill is easier than going up, though we still have to be careful. We make it to the bottom without incident."
    "Bajar la colina es más fácil que subirla, aunque aún tenemos que tener cuidado. Llegamos al fondo sin incidentes."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s10d_f08012ca:

    # "We don’t risk the flashlights until we’re back across the fence and on the trail. Now that we’re not out of bounds, it doesn’t matter if people see us."
    "No nos arriesgamos a usar las linternas hasta que cruzamos de vuelta la cerca y estamos en el sendero. Ahora que no estamos fuera de los límites, no importa si la gente nos ve."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s10d_ce26eafd:

    # Marina "Where do we go now?"
    Marina "Куда мы теперь идем?"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s10d_a1e75b8d:

    # Amber "Hm."
    Amber "Хм."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s10d_4609881e:

    # "I think about it for a moment. There’s not much point in catching up with the tour again. Besides, it’s probably ended by now."
    "Lo pienso por un momento. No tiene mucho sentido alcanzar de nuevo al grupo turístico. Además, probablemente ya terminó."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s10d_220c5309:

    # "Still, if they did notice that we disappeared, then it could be bad for us to just leave the park."
    "Aún así, si notaron que desaparecimos, podría ser malo para nosotras simplemente irnos del parque."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s10d_b40ab934:

    # "The last thing I want to see is our faces on 'Missing Person' posters the next time we stop at a gas station."
    "Lo último que quiero ver son nuestras caras en carteles de 'Personas Desaparecidas' la próxima vez que paremos en una gasolinera."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s10d_10042e08:

    # "But they’ve got a 45 minute lead on us, and that’ll only grow if we were to try to find them."
    "Pero nos llevan 45 minutos de ventaja, y eso solo aumentará si intentamos encontrarlos."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s10d_582dc16d:

    # Amber "We’ll just go back to the parking lot and get outta here. If anyone asks, we can just say we left early."
    Amber "Мы просто вернемся на парковку и уедем отсюда."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s10d_a854a0e4:

    # Marina "Thank God. I was hoping you’d say that."
    Marina "Слава богу. Я надеялась, что ты именно это и скажешь."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s10d_bd326645:

    # Amber "How come?"
    Amber "Ты как?"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s10d_514252ce:

    # Marina "I’m so. {w=0.4} Tired."
    Marina "Я так. {w=0.4} Устала."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s10d_975df1bc:

    # Amber "Same. My back’s gonna hurt for a year."
    Amber "И я. Моя спина будет болеть еще год."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s10d_a9fcd610:

    # Marina "At least you have the comfy bed!"
    Marina "По крайней мере, у тебя есть удобненькая кроватка!"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s10d_69c7800d:

    # Amber "Hey, you could always…"
    Amber "Эй, ну ты всегда можешь…"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s10d_ab45fbbd:

    # Amber "Uh, grab some more pillows from the closet if you need."
    Amber "Э-э, достать еще подушек из шкафчика, если нужно."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s10d_13a0b695:

    # Marina "There are more?"
    Marina "Есть еще подушки?"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s10d_a60865b3:

    # Amber "Oh yeah. Gramps liked to have a zillion pillows when he slept."
    Amber "О да. Дедушка любил спать с кучей подушек."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s10d_8f7a1145:

    # Marina "Oh."
    Marina "Ох."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s10d_e2a7dde8:

    # "She sounds let down. Oops, maybe I shouldn’t have made that connection there."
    "Suena decepcionada. Vaya, quizás no debería haber hecho esa conexión."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s10d_27b10750:

    # Amber "Don’t worry, they weren’t like… His special pillows or anything. You can use them."
    Amber "Не беспокойся, они не были типа…его личными подушками или что-то вроде того. Ты можешь взять их."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s10d_f7c14ffb:

    # Marina "Alright…"
    Marina "Ладно…"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s10d_7458069a:

    # "Damn, she really starts to worry when I mention him. Guess there’s good reason for that."
    "Maldición, realmente empieza a preocuparse cuando lo menciono. Supongo que hay una buena razón para eso."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s10d_9845d5a2:

    # "But right now, though the thought is a familiar jab of sadness, I’m not about to break down. I’m doing okay for now."
    "Pero ahora mismo, aunque el pensamiento es una punzada familiar de tristeza, no voy a derrumbarme. Estoy bien por ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s10d_63c27f86:

    # "We’re quiet the rest of the way down the trail, though. Without having to stick to the slow pace of a guided tour, it’s actually a quick walk."
    "Sin embargo, estamos en silencio el resto del camino por el sendero. Sin tener que seguir el paso lento de un tour guiado, en realidad es una caminata rápida."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s10d_050cb120:

    # "There aren’t any other hikers out, which surprises me. It’s dark, but not that late."
    "No hay otros excursionistas, lo que me sorprende. Está oscuro, pero no es tan tarde."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s10d_36cbb0f1:

    # "As we reach the parking lot, it seems like we had perfect timing. Or maybe perfectly awful."
    "Al llegar al estacionamiento, parece que tuvimos un timing perfecto. O quizás perfectamente horrible."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s10d_44e6b426:

    # "Spilling out of a trailhead on the other side is the tour group that we were briefly part of. I recognize the tour guide, as well as…"
    "Saliendo de un inicio de sendero al otro lado está el grupo turístico del que fuimos parte brevemente. Reconozco al guía, así como a..."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:146
translate spanish hwb_s10d_21d2dceb:

    # Linda "Oh, there you girls are!"
    Linda "А, так вот вы где, девочки!"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s10d_e4e3c10d:

    # "Linda."
    "Linda."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s10d_a9c43696:

    # "She came from my blind spot, before we had time to hide."
    "Vino desde mi punto ciego, antes de que tuviéramos tiempo de escondernos."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s10d_68ace252:

    # "I don’t even try to force a smile as I turn to face her."
    "Ni siquiera intento forzar una sonrisa cuando me giro para enfrentarla."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s10d_0fd408fe:

    # "She strolls up to us, Dino still asleep. Howard’s nowhere to be seen, though. Maybe he’s in their car."
    "Se acerca a nosotras, Dino aún dormido. Howard no se ve por ningún lado, sin embargo. Quizás está en su coche."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:156
translate spanish hwb_s10d_ae08a6b0:

    # Linda "I was hopin’ to see y’all before ya left."
    Linda "Я надеялась увидеть вас, перед тем, как вы уедете."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:160
translate spanish hwb_s10d_07ab27a7:

    # Amber "Yeah, we were pretty tired so we came back early."
    Amber "Ну мы очень устали и решили вернуться пораньше."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s10d_e69567d8:

    # Linda "Oh, I’ll bet you are!"
    Linda "О, бьюсь об заклад, что устали!"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s10d_2b5277c9:

    # "She winks at me, like she’s in on the joke. Problem is, I don’t know what the joke’s supposed to be."
    "Me guiña un ojo, como si estuviera al tanto del chiste. El problema es que no sé cuál se supone que es el chiste."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s10d_8ba659c9:

    # Amber "Uh, what do you mean?"
    Amber "Э-э, что вы имеете в виду?"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s10d_40e3b8c1:

    # Linda "Don’t think I didn’t notice you two running off, now! Figured you were, ya know."
    Linda "Не думайте, что я не заметила, как вы обе сбежали! Подумала, что вы, ну знаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s10d_eea26132:

    # "She laughs and shakes her head."
    "Se ríe y niega con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s10d_1d80812c:

    # Linda "I think that’s good though! Reminds me of me and my Howard when we were younger. We used to sneak off every chance we got, if ya know what I mean!"
    Linda "Вы напоминаете мне меня и моего Говарда в юные годы. Мы то и дело пытались улизнуть, как только подворачивалась возможность, если вы понимаете, о чем я!"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s10d_16716987:

    # "My face starts to turn red as I realize what she’s thinking. Marina’s probably tomato-colored, though I don’t turn to look."
    "Mi cara empieza a ponerse roja cuando me doy cuenta de lo que está pensando. Marina probablemente está color tomate, aunque no me giro para mirar."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s10d_c8141cf9:

    # Amber "We weren’t… Um. I mean, we’re not-"
    Amber "Мы не… Эм. Я имею в виду, мы не-"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s10d_c03987c0:

    # Linda "No need to be embarrassed or anything like that. And besides! At least ya won’t get pregnant!"
    Linda "Да не надо стесняться. И к тому же! По крайне мере вы не забеременеете!"

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s10d_48323ea1:

    # "She laughs heartily, the baby on her chest bouncing with the motion."
    "Se ríe a carcajadas, el bebé en su pecho rebotando con el movimiento."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s10d_ed5caf3e:

    # Linda "Sorry though, I’m gettin’ to be a bit too nosy for my own good. Y’all girls be safe out there. It was nice to get to know ya."
    Linda "Простите меня, я становлюсь что-то слишком любопытной себе же во вред. Осторожней там, девочки. Было приятно познакомиться."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s10d_6d79d126:

    # "She grabs my hand from my side and pumps it in a vigorous handshake, then does the same to Marina. Neither of us react, still dumbfounded."
    "Toma mi mano de mi costado y la agita en un apretón de manos vigoroso, luego hace lo mismo con Marina. Ninguna de las dos reacciona, aún atónitas."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s10d_e748387a:

    # "Then she heads off towards the sea of cars. More of a puddle now, since most have already left."
    "Luego se dirige hacia el mar de coches. Más bien un charco ahora, ya que la mayoría ya se han ido."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s10d_299ab05b:

    # "I turn to Marina. As expected, her face is scarlet."
    "Me giro hacia Marina. Como era de esperar, tiene la cara roja como un tomate."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s10d_c86f1d2f:

    # Marina "Um. Wow."
    Marina "Эм. Вот это да."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s10d_131f8310:

    # Amber "Right? That poor baby."
    Amber "Вот уж точно. Бедный ребенок."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s10d_87c04551:

    # Amber "And that poor husband."
    Amber "И бедный муж."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s10d_434cd12d:

    # Marina "I didn’t think people like that were real. Like, that they only existed in books and movies and stuff."
    Marina "Я и не думала, что такие люди правда существуют. То есть, думала, что они бывают в книгах и фильмах или типа того."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:228
translate spanish hwb_s10d_2b5ed0be:

    # Amber "About that existential talk..."
    Amber "К теме об экзистенциальном разговоре..."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:232
translate spanish hwb_s10d_0945f7a5:

    # Amber "They say the desert does weird things to your head."
    Amber "Говорят, что в пустыне что-то странное происходит с головой."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:236
translate spanish hwb_s10d_cdd5cd70:

    # Amber "Or maybe Wisconsin does."
    Amber "А может это все из-за Висконсина."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s10d_bce08ae4:

    # "I shrug, and start walking back towards the RV. I’m glad that Marina doesn’t push the topic of Linda’s… misconception."
    "Me encojo de hombros y empiezo a caminar de vuelta a la casa rodante. Me alegra que Marina no insista en el tema del... malentendido de Linda."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s10d_8f940c61:

    # "I unlock the door and let Marina in first. We’re one of the last ones here."
    "Abro la puerta y dejo entrar a Marina primero. Somos de las últimas en llegar aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s10d_63371e53:

    # "Before I pull the door shut, I take a final look around Canyon de Chelly. Or what little of it I can see."
    "Antes de cerrar la puerta, echo un último vistazo al Cañón de Chelly. O a lo poco que puedo ver de él."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s10d_f630158a:

    # "It may have been a bust, but like Marina said…"
    "Puede que haya sido un fracaso, pero como dijo Marina..."

# game/script/hwb_s10d.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s10d_36b525c4:

    # "It wasn’t a total waste of time."
    "No fue una pérdida total de tiempo."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s10d.rpy:47
    old "Going down the hill"
    new "Going down the hill"

    # script/hwb_s10d.rpy:139
    old "Walking"
    new "Walking"

